# Versioning

- **Single source:** `package.json` `"version"` field — [SemVer 2.0](https://semver.org/) (`MAJOR.MINOR.PATCH`).
- **Runtime:** `src/utils/app-version.ts` re-exports `pkg.version` for `/api/version`.
- **Bump when:** merge-worthy code changes (features, fixes, breaking changes). Skip docs-only or trivial edits.
- **How to bump:**
  - PATCH (bug fixes): `npm run version:patch`
  - MINOR (features): `npm run version:minor`
  - MAJOR (breaking): `npm run version:major`
- **Do not** maintain per-file version headers; use Git history instead.

See `planner/semver-version-migration.md` for migration notes.
